article.description: — Quincy Olivari scored a career-high 43 points and Xavier romped to a 93-68 victory over DePaul on Saturday, handing the Blue Demons their 10th straight loss.
article.headline: Olivari scores career-high 43, Xavier routs DePaul 93-68
article.linkText: Olivari scores career-high 43, Xavier routs DePaul 93-68
article.story: CHICAGO -- — Quincy Olivari scored a career-high 43 points and Xavier romped to a 93-68 victory over DePaul on Saturday, handing the Blue Demons their 10th straight loss. Olivari added 10 rebounds and three steals for the Musketeers (12-10, 6-5 Big East Conference). Desmond Claude had 15 points and five rebounds. Dayvion McKnight scored 11. The Blue Demons (3-19, 0-11) were led by Jaden Henley with 17 points. Churchill Abass added 13 points, nine rebounds and two blocks. K.T. Raimey scored 12. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
